lead_paragraph: Singapore does not want to host an annual Formula One grand prix anymore, F1 CEO Bernie Ecclestone told German magazine Auto Motor und Sport, casting doubt on the future of Formula One in Southeast Asia as Malaysia is also considering pulling out.

headline.print_headline: Ecclestone Says Singapore Wants to Drop F1 Race: Report
